# Main OpenFRDB Page
## What is OpenFRDB?
OpenFRDB is an Open Facial Recognition Database powered by OpenCV and the OpenSource Community.  Please see the [Wiki](https://github.com/openfrdb/OpenFRDB/wiki) for more details.
